name: Self
description: We have already seen that it stands for the True self and appearance. It is also referred to as the house of Self.

name: Wealth
description: Income, family, primary education, and the promises that one keeps. It represents the comforts related to the first house.

name: Efforts
description: Courage, energy levels, and younger brother. It includes the courage to face problems.

name: Family
description: Education, mother, your house, vehicles, and comfort levels. It signifies home and family.

name: Kids
description: Children, intelligence, and karmic effects in this birth. It talks about art, culture, and the enjoyments and hobbies of people. It holds in account everyday responsibilities.

name: Job, Debts and disease
description: Debts and disease. It signifies the difficulties one goes through at an early age of life.

name: Spouse, Partner, Business
description: Spouse, partner in business, and relationships. It gives the information about the individual's relationship with other people.

name: Obsession, Longevity, Sudden Downfall
description: Longevity, sudden downfall, secrets in life, litigation, and imprisonment.

name: Luck
description: Bhagyasthan, father, higher studies, thinking ability, and good deeds. It signifies the philosophical and the learning side of the individual.

name: Action Job
description: Karmasthan, profession, and career. It is a good placement for public life and profession.

name: Support
description: House of profits, elder brother, and second marriage. It signifies social networking and wish fulfilment of an individual.

name: Expense
description: House of expenditure, death, moksha, sorrows, incarceration, and loneliness. It also signifies the subconscious of an individual.
